== Correct school ? ==

{{OTRS talk|issue=|otrs=2015042710011054}}
I've had an OTRS contact that brings into doubt his school. There is a plaque on the side of the Seville State School that states he attended that school along with his two brothers. Yet the  Australian Dictionary of Biography states he went to Lilydale. Perhaps he attended both ? - [[User:Peripitus |Peripitus]] [[User talk:Peripitus|(Talk)]] 10:50, 3 May 2015 (UTC)
:It is, of course, possible that he attended both. However, I don't believe I have seen mention elsewhere that he attended the Seville State School. Cheers, [[User:Abraham, B.S.|Abraham, B.S.]] ([[User talk:Abraham, B.S.|talk]]) 01:25, 4 May 2015 (UTC)
